#

Crispy Skin Salmon with Lemon Dill Sauce

$18.99
550 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

FishDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carb

Tags:

SeafoodHealthyQuick Meal

Description

A delightful combination of crispy salmon skin paired with a refreshing lemon dill sauce, served with sautéed asparagus.

Ingredients

  • Salmon fillets: 2 pieces
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • Fresh dill: 1 tablespoon, chopped
  • Asparagus: 1 bunch
  • Butter: 1 tablespoon
